title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 3 2022

description:
Dishonest ads run by Democrats against Kansas abortion measure. Manchin lies about his vote on the Schumer spending bill. Teacher tells us middle school kids are changing their pronouns all the time like singer Demi Lovato, who just switched back to she/her and they/them from just they/them. Manchin fights with NBC's Andrea Mitchell over endorsing Biden in 2024. Peter Doocy takes it to Kirby on Zawahiri and Afghanistan. The Inflation Reduction Act doesn't.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
